        <p>Lets you select a style from a style sheet, applying that style to the content selected in the topic<MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Contributor"> or document</MadCap:conditionalText>. It is the only button in the Text Format Toolbar that deals with style formatting as opposed to local (or "inline") formatting. <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare">You can also select a style class for content from the Styles window pane. For more information see <MadCap:xref href="../../../Styles/About_Styles_and_Style_Sheets.htm" target="" title="" alt="">About Styles and Stylesheets</MadCap:xref>.</MadCap:conditionalText></p>
